next comm chrono: E
next unread comm: F
reply to current comment: R
parent of current comment: P
history (modlog) of current comment: M
hide history: X
skip to end (last): V
skip to top (first): T
get more comments: G
lower top threshold: [
raise top threshold: ]
lower bottom threshold: ,
raise bottom threshold: .
toggle d2 widget: /
